# Headphone Company Website

This project is a  web page for a headphone company, designed to be responsive and nice looking. 

## Features

- The Design Responsive: The layout  will automatically adjusts based on screen size, with a mobile-friendly version for screens 480px or smaller.
- Fonts Used: The website uses the Source Sans Pro and Spin Cycle OT to make it nice looking.
- Interactive Elements: Links and buttons change appearance when hovered on or clicked.

## Development Language Used

- HTML
- CSS

## Setup

1. Clone the repository.
2. Ensure you have the fonts Source Sans Pro and Spin Cycle OT installed on your system.
3. Open `index.html` in your web browser to view the site.

## Interaction Notes

- Links change to #FF6565 when hovered or active.
- Buttons reduce opacity to 0.9 when hovered or active.
- Maximum width of content is set to 1000px and is centered on the page.

